lead_paragraph: Four-time major winner Rory McIlroy roared back into contention at the French Open on Friday, sinking six birdies in a 5-under round of 66 to join a five-way share of the lead.

headline.print_headline: Rory McIlroy Roars Back to Share 5-Way Lead at French Open
